snippet.title: RealArcade November Day #16 | Qbeez 2 Longplay (Quest Mode)
snippet.description:
Playing one random game from RealArcade throughout November.
Day #16 and it's Qbeez 2 by Skunk Studios.
———————————————————————————————
The longest video I have ever made. (Plus some pauses inbetween the video) 

Day #17: Shape Shifter
———————————————————————————————
RealArcade Games Preservation Project: https://archive.org/details/realrcade-games-preservation-project

Qbeez 2 (Skunk Studios): http://www.skunkstudios.com/

Also it's TheBowlFoSho's (The current owner of RGPP) birthday. So that's why i'm playing Qbeez 2. (His favorite game)
